[{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0245","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0245.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0269","title":"GNU Emacs 本地窃听漏洞","description":"GNU Emacs 20 版本在启动新子进程时，未能正确设置从属伪终端（PTY）设备的权限，导致本地用户能够读取或修改 Emacs 与子进程之间的通信内容。该漏洞影响 GNU Emacs 20 版本，攻击者需具备本地系统访问权限，通过访问权限不当的 PTY 设备文件，可窃听或篡改 Emacs 与其子进程（如 Shell、编译器等）间的交互数据，导致信息泄露或进程控制劫持。攻击者需拥有本地账户权限，利用 PTY 权限配置缺陷实施窃听或篡改攻击。CVSS 评分 2.1，属低危本地信息泄露漏洞。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0269"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-18T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:21.877","remediation":"建议升级到 GNU Emacs 20.2 或更高版本（可通过官方 ftp.gnu.org 下载源码重新编译安装，或使用发行版提供的更新包），该版本修复了启动子进程时从伪终端（PTY）从设备权限设置不当的问题，将 slave PTY 权限由可被同机其他本地用户读写的 0666 改为仅属主可读写的 0600 并正确设置属主。对于无法立即升级的环境，临时缓解措施为：避免在本机多用户共享环境下于 Emacs 中运行含敏感信息的 shell 命令或交互式子进程；通过限制 /dev/pty* 与 /dev/ttyp* 设备节点的默认权限（如由系统管理员将相应设备权限收紧为 0600）降低被其他本地用户窃听或篡改通信的风险；也可改用 screen 或 tmux 等已正确设置 PTY 权限的终端复用器来运行子进程。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1125","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&date=2000-04-15&msg=tg4s8zioxq.fsf%40mercury.rus.uni-stuttgart.de","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/7e65fa522cff0172990568230ff9b719b8650296/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0269.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0269","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0269.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f6fc85c731fb3018b2c4fbe9aed66186edd5321b/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0269.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/5d945305f2cad48b7bb06af582393a58c31555d3/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-j2cr-8pw5-rpvq/GHSA-j2cr-8pw5-rpvq.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0269.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--6a1643ae-483e-40ad-b0a7-710021ff3bd4.json","https://github.com/dong-xs/Vul-PAG/blob/7eb3b32094a5270cfd8495366e0e4a7df5a874ce/aspect_prediction/org_pred_diff.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/ce9ef916bfcfa71e15bd79861b0ea3312f7ed373/2000.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0245.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0239","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0239.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0266","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9127,\"outputTokens\":21,\"totalTokens\":10812}}","description":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 5.01 存在跨框架安全策略绕过漏洞。其 Java 实现中的 JSObject 接口未对网页小程序与文档对象模型（DOM）的交互进行充分限制，远程攻击者可通过构造恶意的 Java Applet，借助 JSObject 修改 DOM 属性，将 IFRAME 框架的源设置为任意 JavaScript URL，从而绕过浏览器同源策略与跨框架安全限制。攻击需诱导受害者访问恶意网页并加载该 Applet，成功利用后攻击者可在受害者浏览器上下文中执行脚本、读取受限内容或发起进一步攻击。该漏洞影响运行 IE 5.01 的系统，CVSS 评分约为 2.6，危害等级较低，属于安全策略绕过类问题。","severity":"LOW","score":2.6,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0266"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-18T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:21.387","remediation":"建议立即将 Internet Explorer 升级至 5.5 或更高版本，并安装 Microsoft 发布的安全更新补丁（如 2000 年 4 月发布的累积安全修补程序）。如暂时无法升级，可在 IE「Internet 选项→安全」中将安全级别调至「高」，禁用 Java  applet 运行与脚本对 DOM 的跨框架访问，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1121","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=38FC6130.D6D178FD%40nat.bg","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2126251525a2d370ea93bd7affc3a9b71b419b4c/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0266.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0266","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0266.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/7aedbd0209e609a1924ad29a8dda684737576137/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0266.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/5d945305f2cad48b7bb06af582393a58c31555d3/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-4fm7-p9w2-qjwr/GHSA-4fm7-p9w2-qjwr.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0266.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152300_152400.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idbypass","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/ce9ef916bfcfa71e15bd79861b0ea3312f7ed373/2000.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0239.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0069","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0069.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0083","title":"HP-UX asecure 音频安全文件权限配置不当漏洞","description":"HP-UX 操作系统中 asecure 组件在创建音频安全文件 /var/adm/audio.sec 时设置了不安全的文件权限，导致本地攻击者可通过修改或替换该文件触发拒绝服务或获取额外系统权限。该漏洞影响 HP-UX 多个版本，攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限，利用难度较低，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0083"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-18","updated":"2026-07-18","remediation":"升级 HP-UX 至对应补丁版本：10.20 安装 PHSS_14055、11.00 安装 PHSS_14056、11i 安装 PHSS_14057 或更高版本；或通过执行 chmod 600 /var/adm/audio.sec 将音频安全文件权限修正为仅 root 可读写；临时缓解可禁用 asecure 服务或限制本地用户访问音频设备。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/986","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/3921.php","http://hp.com/security/security-warnings/2000/hpsbux0004-118.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0069.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0238","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0238.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0265","title":"Panda Security Panda Security 3.0 安全软件绕过漏洞","description":"Panda Security 3.0 反病毒软件在安装时注册了“添加/删除程序”小程序（Add/Remove Programs）中的卸载入口，但未对该卸载操作进行充分的权限校验或身份认证。本地已登录的普通用户可利用操作系统自带的“添加/删除程序”小程序直接触发卸载流程，从而无需管理员授权即可移除 Panda Security 安全软件。受影响范围为运行 Panda Security 3.0 的 Windows 系统，攻击条件为攻击者需在目标主机上拥有本地登录会话及普通用户权限。成功利用后，目标系统将丧失该安全软件提供的防护能力，使主机暴露于恶意软件威胁之下，CVSS 评分为 4.6，危害等级为中。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0265"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-17T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:21.267","remediation":"立即将 Panda Security 防护软件升级至官方已修复该问题的后续版本（3.0 之后的补丁版本），并通过组策略或本地安全策略限制普通用户访问\"控制面板→添加/删除程序\"，或使用管理员权限限制对 Panda 卸载注册表项（如 HKLM\\Software\\Microsoft\\Windows\\CurrentVersion\\Uninstall 下对应项）的写入权限，防止未授权用户卸载防护软件。如暂无法升级，可对涉及 Panda 安装目录与卸载入口设置 NTFS 权限仅允许管理员操作作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://updates.pandasoftware.com/docs/us/Avoidvulnerability.zip","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1119","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=38FB45F2.550EA000%40teleline.es","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2126251525a2d370ea93bd7affc3a9b71b419b4c/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0265.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0265","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0265.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d281505551869bb381f43b6d1c6cb3abf45ad885/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0265.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/5d945305f2cad48b7bb06af582393a58c31555d3/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-m5vc-rmmh-7r76/GHSA-m5vc-rmmh-7r76.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0265.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152300_152400.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--acda5f15-ab03-494b-b04f-3708fa451787.json","https://github.com/Christopher0129/security-knowledge-base/blob/ecec748afe5bbe2fcd2fd04b00fb46bc827b2c5d/system-vulnerabilities/macos.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0238.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0237","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0237.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0264","title":"Panda Security 3.0 注册表绕过权限提升漏洞","description":"Panda Security 3.0 存在访问控制绕过漏洞，其原理在于该软件在禁用注册表编辑功能后，未能对注册表的实际写入操作实施有效限制。本地攻击者无需绕过额外的身份认证机制，即可通过直接执行 .reg 注册表文件或采用其他替代方式修改注册表内容，从而绕过软件的安全防护策略并提升自身权限。该漏洞影响 Panda Security 3.0 版本，攻击者利用成功后可篡改系统关键配置、破坏安全软件的防护能力。CVSS 评分为 2.1，危害等级为低危，利用条件要求攻击者具备目标系统的本地访问权限。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0264"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-04-17T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:21.143","remediation":"建议立即升级至 WatchGuard Endpoint Security 最新版本（现 Panda Security 已并入 WatchGuard）。若无法升级，请通过组策略禁用 .reg 文件关联（regedit /s 禁用），并通过组策略“阻止访问注册表编辑工具”加固注册表访问控制，同时部署应用程序控制策略禁止未签名可执行文件运行。建议尽快更换为现代终端防护产品以获得持续安全更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://updates.pandasoftware.com/docs/us/Avoidvulnerability.zip","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1119","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=38FB45F2.550EA000%40teleline.es","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19855","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/7e65fa522cff0172990568230ff9b719b8650296/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0264.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0264","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0264.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/7aedbd0209e609a1924ad29a8dda684737576137/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0264.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/5d945305f2cad48b7bb06af582393a58c31555d3/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-2322-3mhq-32v4/GHSA-2322-3mhq-32v4.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0264.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152300_152400.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_1.list.dict","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001294.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0237.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0281","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0281.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0291","title":"StarDivision StarOffice 5.1 缓冲区溢出拒绝服务漏洞","description":"StarOffice 5.1 存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，攻击者可在文档中嵌入超长 URL，当用户打开精心构造的恶意文档时，会触发缓冲区溢出导致 StarOffice 程序崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞依赖用户交互触发，攻击者需通过社会工程学手段诱使用户打开特制文档，无法远程主动利用。影响 StarOffice 5.1 版本，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。建议用户避免打开来源不明的文档以降低风险。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0291"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-16T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:24.650","remediation":"升级到 StarOffice 5.2 或更高版本，该漏洞在后续版本中已修复。由于 StarOffice 已停止维护，建议迁移至开源的 LibreOffice 或 Apache OpenOffice 替代。同时避免打开来源不明的文档，防止嵌入恶意超长 URL 触发缓冲区溢出。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-04/0077.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1112"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0281.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0254","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0254.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0286","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9130,\"outputTokens\":20,\"totalTokens\":10814}}","description":"X Window 系统的字体服务器 xfs 存在输入验证缺陷，本地用户可向 xfs 服务器发送畸形（格式错误的）输入数据，触发服务异常并导致拒绝服务，使依赖该字体服务的图形界面无法正常工作。该漏洞影响运行 xfs 的 Linux 系统（如 RedHat Linux 6.x 等）。攻击条件为攻击者需具备本地系统访问权限，通过构造特制请求发送至 xfs 服务端口即可利用，造成目标系统字体服务崩溃。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0286"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-16T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:23.993","remediation":"升级至 RedHat Linux 6.x 的 xfs 相关补丁 rpm 包（如 XFree86-xfs-3.3.6-11 及以上），并通过 chkconfig 或 ntsysv 关闭 xfs 字体服务（执行 `chkconfig xfs off` 并停止服务）；在无法立即打补丁时，通过防火墙限制仅本地回环访问 7100 端口，禁止远程主机向 xfs 发送畸形输入。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-04/0079.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1111","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19850","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/7481e97cf7b60a5b982d99d7dad1ea61174940fb/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0286.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0286","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0286.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/bc48b6c04c59ceff2d71da45cd843fc1d449dc48/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0286.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-f7wv-vgh8-m4x4/GHSA-f7wv-vgh8-m4x4.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x2000/1111/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0286.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--d7137e10-a43e-4634-8e47-c443d968d8c5.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/1216817b1ffea775aa09a87ad4eb5d4ec3f12b57/2000.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0254.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0253","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0253.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0284","title":"华盛顿大学 imapd IMAP 服务缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"华盛顿大学（University of Washington）开发的 IMAP 服务程序 imapd 4.7 版本存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。已通过身份认证、拥有合法邮箱账户的用户，可向服务器发送超长的 LIST 等 IMAP 命令，使服务端在处理命令参数时发生缓冲区溢出，进而覆盖返回地址并执行任意命令。该漏洞影响运行 WU-IMAP 4.7 的邮件服务器，攻击前提是攻击者需具备一个有效的系统账户，利用方式是通过构造畸形 IMAP 命令触发溢出实现权限提升或远程命令执行。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0284"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-16T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:23.750","remediation":"立即将 University of Washington imapd 升级至 4.7c2（2000.287 之后的修复版本）或更高版本（建议升级到 2000.315 及以上）。如无法立即升级，可在防火墙/ACL 上限制仅允许受信任 IP 访问 TCP 143 端口的 IMAP 服务，并禁用匿名或低权限账户的远程登录，同时启用 tcp_wrappers 限制访问来源作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-04/0074.html","http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-04/0085.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1110","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19847","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dde4d96d7c1eff197b9a15817af615500736afa7/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0284.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0284","https://github.com/e-m-b-a/emba/blob/ffab8835dab57629dd708bbd389c0fd0b4f23ace/config/msf_cve-db.txt","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0284.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/bc48b6c04c59ceff2d71da45cd843fc1d449dc48/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0284.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/2118.txt","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-rj56-vwqm-8wv9/GHSA-rj56-vwqm-8wv9.json","https://github.com/Chudry/Xerror/blob/07ec57cabcd27cdb47c89af452bdf4ed07207347/xerror/parsing/msf_module_result/msf_module_cve.txt","https://github.com/openctibr/threatFeeds/blob/2d918d16364c8b9e6090c92b807ccd619223575d/ExploitableVulnerabilitiesFeed.txt","https://github.com/bailehang/snort_2.2.0/blob/34f8a3a85f15645aea53d6e0d46863c7c57e43ef/doc/signatures/2106.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0253.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0236","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0236.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0263","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":16317,\"outputTokens\":32,\"totalTokens\":16349}}","description":"Red Hat Linux 6.x 的 X 字体服务器 (xfs) 存在拒绝服务及缓冲区溢出漏洞，源于字体服务器未正确处理畸形字体请求。远程未认证攻击者可向 X 字体服务端口（默认 7100/tcp）发送精心构造的畸形请求，触发缓冲区溢出或服务崩溃，导致拒绝服务甚至潜在的代码执行。该漏洞影响运行 X 字体服务的 Red Hat Linux 6.x 系统，攻击者无需认证即可远程发起攻击，CVSS 评分 2.1，属低危级别。Red Hat 已发布补丁修复该漏洞，建议升级至修复版本或禁用不必要的 X 字体服务。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0263"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-16T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:21.020","remediation":"建议立即升级到 Red Hat Linux 6.2 附带的 xfs 修复版本（执行 `rpm -Uvh xfs-*.rpm` 或通过 `up2date xfs` 安装官方补丁）。若无法立即升级，可在 /etc/X11/fs/config 中将 `no-listen = tcp` 设为开启并注释掉 `port = 7100`，仅允许本地 Unix socket 访问，同时用防火墙阻断 7100 端口的外来连接，并停止非必要的 xfs 服务（`/etc/rc.d/init.d/xfs stop`）作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-04/0079.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1111","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2126251525a2d370ea93bd7affc3a9b71b419b4c/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0263.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0263","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0263.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d281505551869bb381f43b6d1c6cb3abf45ad885/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0263.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/424512debdca84cc53ffa1fb3810a74f7b1905a5/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-fjx2-c7c3-8w5j/GHSA-fjx2-c7c3-8w5j.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x2000/1111/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0263.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--df86b5a3-4715-4230-9e82-a029e91666eb.json","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_dos.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0236.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0273","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0273.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0285","title":"XFree86 X11R6 -xkbmap 参数缓冲区溢出本地代码执行漏洞","description":"XFree86 3.3.x 版本（X11R6 相关实现）在处理 X 服务器命令行参数时，对 -xkbmap 参数的长度未做充分边界校验，存在栈缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可在启动 X 服务器时传入超长的 -xkbmap 参数，覆盖栈上返回地址或关键数据，进而以 X 服务器的权限（通常为 root）执行任意命令，实现本地提权。该漏洞的攻击条件为攻击者需具备本地访问权限并能控制 X 服务器的启动命令行参数。CVSS 评分约 7.2，危害等级为高危，可导致权限提升与任意代码执行。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0285"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-16","updated":"2026-07-19","remediation":"将 XFree86 升级至已修复该问题的 3.3.6 版本或 4.0 及以上发行版；若暂时无法升级，应移除 X 服务器二进制文件的 setuid 权限（chmod u-s /usr/X11R6/bin/X），并限制普通本地用户启动 X 服务器及使用 -xkbmap 参数的能力，以阻断本地提权利用路径。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-04/0076.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1306","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/main/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0285.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/main/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-989m-9h73-8xcc/GHSA-989m-9h73-8xcc.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0273.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0806","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0806.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0260","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":10856,\"outputTokens\":24,\"totalTokens\":10880}}","description":"Microsoft Visual InterDev 1.0 中的 dvwssr.dll 动态链接库存在缓冲区溢出漏洞（亦称\"Link View 服务端组件\"漏洞）。该组件在处理用户请求时未对输入文件名的长度进行充分边界校验，攻击者在未身份认证的情况下，可通过向运行该组件的 IIS 服务器发送特制的超长文件名请求，溢出栈缓冲区，从而触发拒绝服务或执行任意命令。受影响范围包括安装了 FrontPage 98 Server Extensions 的 IIS 服务器及 Microsoft InterDev 1.0 环境，攻击仅需网络可达目标 Web 服务即可远程利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0260"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-04-14T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:20.640","remediation":"建议立即升级 Microsoft Visual InterDev 至 1.0 SP1 或更高版本，并安装 Microsoft 2000 年 4 月发布的安全补丁（MS00-025）。同时升级 FrontPage 98 Server Extensions 到最新版本。如暂无法打补丁，可在 IIS 中临时移除或禁用 dvwssr.dll（Link View Server-Side Component）对应的 ISAPI 扩展映射，并限制对 /_vti_bin/ 目录的匿名访问作为缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/282","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1109","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/2000/ms00-025","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19845","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2126251525a2d370ea93bd7affc3a9b71b419b4c/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0260.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0260","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0260.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d281505551869bb381f43b6d1c6cb3abf45ad885/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0260.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/967.txt","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/frontpage_dvwssr.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0260.json","https://github.com/jdkoftinoff/mb-linux-msli/blob/8adb103e34af9ff1d8d122e9ee2a1808836f0a14/uClinux-dist/user/snort/drop-rules/sid-msg.map","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/slacker247/GPDA/blob/fa9006d0877a691f1ddffe88799c844a3e8a669a/Aries/Sodi/Run/IDSrules/rule.975"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0806.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2000/EXP-AVE-2000-0806.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0806.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0229","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0229.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0254","title":"Dansie Shopping Cart cart.pl 购物数据库与配置信息泄露漏洞","description":"Dansie Shopping Cart 3.0.4 版本的 cart.pl 脚本存在信息泄露漏洞。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过在 URL 中引用 env、db 或 vars 等表单变量的方式，直接获取目标系统的购物车数据库及配置文件信息。该漏洞影响使用该版本购物车系统的网站，攻击者无需登录即可利用，可导致敏感数据泄露。建议升级到更高版本或应用官方补丁。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0254"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-04-14T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:19.827","remediation":"建议将 Dansie Shopping Cart 升级至最新可用版本，或彻底删除 cart.pl 脚本并替换为官方更新的电子商务平台。若暂无法升级，应在 Web 服务器配置（如 Apache .htaccess）中添加规则拒绝对 cart.pl 的远程访问，并删除或重命名含有 env、db、vars 参数的调试接口，同时在防火墙层面限制对该脚本的 HTTP 请求。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1115","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/4954","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19852","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2126251525a2d370ea93bd7affc3a9b71b419b4c/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0254.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0254","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0254.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d281505551869bb381f43b6d1c6cb3abf45ad885/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0254.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/424512debdca84cc53ffa1fb3810a74f7b1905a5/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-v93j-3f23-p5mq/GHSA-v93j-3f23-p5mq.json","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/dansie_cart.nasl","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cwe_details/cwe_details_300_400.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0254.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001287.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--4c93c92e-6eca-4fb4-a659-77bb57267063.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0229.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2000/EXP-AVE-2000-0229.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0229.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0226","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0226.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0250","title":"QSSL QNX 4.25 A crypt() 弱加密本地权限提升漏洞","description":"QNX 4.25 操作系统中的 crypt() 密码加密函数采用了安全性极弱的加密算法，无法提供足够的密码保护强度。已登录系统的本地用户可利用该弱加密机制的缺陷，对系统中存储的密码哈希进行解密还原，从而获取其他用户（包括特权用户）的明文口令。该漏洞影响运行 QNX 4.25 A 版本的系统，攻击前提是攻击者需先获得目标主机的本地访问权限（如低权限用户账户），通过本地执行解密操作即可实现权限提升，危害系统账户安全。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0250"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-04-14T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:19.307","remediation":"建议升级至 QNX 4.25 B 或更高版本（QSSL 已发布修复补丁），或应用 QSSL 官方发布的 crypt() 补丁包。若暂时无法升级，可通过限制本地账号登录权限、启用影子密码文件、配置更强的密码策略（如最小长度 12 位、复杂度要求）作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-04/0072.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1114","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19851","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2126251525a2d370ea93bd7affc3a9b71b419b4c/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0250.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0250","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0250.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d281505551869bb381f43b6d1c6cb3abf45ad885/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0250.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/424512debdca84cc53ffa1fb3810a74f7b1905a5/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-p3hr-r8ch-hrrq/GHSA-p3hr-r8ch-hrrq.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x2000/1114/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0250.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Exploit-List-Ja/blob/b82432e7d59d95db9f183c0cefa7744595784afa/2000.tsv","https://github.com/williamjsmail/piranha/blob/e60f12e6edcde8585ee473f701c2421f6efe72d9/CVE2CAPEC/database/CVE-2000.jsonl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0226.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0270","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0270.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0283","title":"SGI IRIX Performance Copilot 信息泄露漏洞","description":"IRIX 系统中默认安装的 Performance Copilot（性能监控工具）包含一个安全配置缺陷，其 pmcd 守护进程在默认配置下未对远程访问进行适当限制。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过网络连接到目标主机上监听的 pmcd 服务端口，进而读取包括系统运行状态、进程信息、硬件指标等在内的敏感系统信息。该漏洞影响采用默认安装方式且启用 Performance Copilot 的 SGI IRIX 操作系统，攻击条件仅为攻击者能够与目标的 pmcd 服务建立网络连接，无需任何凭据或本地权限，利用方式是通过标准的 pmcd 协议请求获取本不应暴露的系统内部数据，可能导致信息泄露并辅助后续攻击。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0283"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-12T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:23.630","remediation":"建议升级 IRIX 至已修复该问题的补丁版本（SGI 官方补丁 4107 及以上，对应 IRIX 6.5.7m 或更新版本）。若无法立即升级，可停止 pmcd 守护进程（/etc/init.d/pmcd stop）或修改 /etc/perf/pmcd.options 限制仅本地访问，并在防火墙屏蔽 TCP 端口 4321（pmcd），仅放行受信任主机作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-04/0056.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1106","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dde4d96d7c1eff197b9a15817af615500736afa7/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0283.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0283","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0283.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/3d905f6009ce1a0cb55b6b90198454d955586615/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0283.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/irix_copilot.nasl","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-r4wv-238c-4wf9/GHSA-r4wv-238c-4wf9.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152300_152400.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--4f831d0f-2945-4421-89cd-6f0917b597ee.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001284.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0270.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0255","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0255.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0287","title":"CNC Technology BizDB 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"CNC Technology BizDB 1.0 的 bizdb-search.cgi 脚本存在远程命令执行漏洞，由于对 dbname 参数中的 shell 元字符过滤不严，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的 HTTP 请求，注入系统命令并执行任意代码。攻击者无需认证即可利用该漏洞完全控制受影响服务器，危害严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0287"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-04-12T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:24.117","remediation":"BizDB 1.0 已停止维护且厂商 CNC Technology 不再提供安全更新，建议立即从 Web 服务器根目录移除或重命名 bizdb-search.cgi 脚本，或直接卸载 BizDB 软件；如业务必须使用，需在 Web 服务器（Apache/Nginx）层面限制该脚本的执行权限并启用严格的输入过滤规则，禁止 dbname 参数包含 shell 元字符。最彻底的方案是替换为仍在维护的数据库管理系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-04/0058.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1104","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19844"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0255.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0255.toml"}]